name: Reggae Life
description:
I never listened to many songs but when I started going out I discovered new genres and one of them is reggae, I remember like it was yesterday one of the first reggae "festivals" I went to in Favela do Sapé, a relatively small community in São Paulo - Brazil. Despite the location and the music played there, it was still one of the best experiences I had and today I carry this experience appreciating works of sound art.
Music: Bob Marley - Natural Mystic.
